SLADE3 is a modern editor for Doom-engine based games and source ports.
It has the ability to view, modify, and write many different
game-specific formats, and even convert between some of them, or from/to
other generic formats such as PNG.

SLADE has many different features, allowing for a simple yet
comprehensive editing experience:

	- Basic archive/resource editing
	- Simple tabbed interface
	- Many supported game formats
	- Map editing
	- Advanced text editor
	- Graphic conversion
	- Texture editing
